### Token Obtain (Login)
POST /token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}

### Token Refresh
POST /token/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

### Logout (Blacklist Refresh Token)
POST /logout/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "refresh_token": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

### User: List Users
GET /utilisateur/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### User: Get User Detail (replace :id)
GET /utilisateur/:id/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### User: Create User
POST /utilisateur/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "tel": 1234567890,
  "profile": "client",
  "password": "newuserpassword",
  "code": "",
  "a_restaurant": false,
  "a_boutique": false,
  "quartier": "Quartier Example"
}

